It pains me to say this a little bit, because Python is a great language, and overall a better ecosystem than R.

But R's Tidyverse sets the bar for data science and analytics.

#Python #rstats #datascience

Generally, trying to learn more than one programming language at a time will cause problems.

Your memory of one language will interfere with your memory of the other.

(For example "filter" in Python vs "filter" in R)

#rstats #Python #programming #learntocode https://t.co/OiHl8YAUDM

Not to mention, you'll constantly be comparing one language to the other.

I honestly do compare Python to R quite a bit when I use it.

(I typically want Python's data tools to be more like the Tidyverse)

#rstats #programming #Python

This applies to data science just as much as basketball.

Master the fundamentals, and the level of everything else will rise.
